# 🎨 Graphika Designs

**Graphika Designs** is a modern, fully responsive landing page designed to help athletes stand out with bold, professional visual identity.

## ✨ Why this project was built

As the sports scene grows in Mozambique, many talented athletes still lack impactful digital presence. I built this landing page to empower them with a platform that reflects their potential — visual strength, credibility, and creative storytelling all in one place.

## 🧰 Tech Stack

- **HTML5** — semantic markup optimized for SEO
- **CSS3** — Flexbox layout, scalable design
- **Mobile-First Design** — seamless on all devices
- **Creative UX/UI** — clean interface with subtle motion
- **WhatsApp CTA** — direct client conversion built in

## 💼 Features

- Sections: Hero, About, Services, Testimonials and Contact
- Styled image gallery with responsive interaction
- Accessible, high-contrast layout for all devices
- Ready for SEO, client engagement, and scalability

